%I A394616 #19 Jul 14 2026 23:54:23
%S A394616 0,1,3,16,209,10806,3569509
%N A394616 Number of strict non-grounded 2-ary convexities on a set of n elements.
%C A394616 A convexity G on a set X is n-ary if its convex sets are precisely the sets A with the property that co(B) is a subset of A for each subset B with cardinality no more than n. A strict non-grounded convexity is one that does not contain an empty set.
%D A394616 M. L. J. van de Vel, Theory of Convex Structures, North-Holland Mathematical Library, vol. 50, North-Holland, Amsterdam, 1993.
%H A394616 Daniil Naumikhin, <a href="https://github.com/SofaaSogo-oh/2gar-code">Enumeration of binary Convex Structures</a>, GitHub repository.
%e A394616 For n=2 the a(2)=3 strict non-grounded binary convexities are following:
%e A394616   {{0, 1}, {0}},
%e A394616   {{0, 1}, {1}},
%e A394616   {{0, 1}}.
%Y A394616 Cf. A326878, A000798, A394095.
%K A394616 nonn,hard,more,new
%O A394616 0,3
%A A394616 _Daniil Naumikhin_ and _Aidar Dulliev_, Jun 18 2026
